{"timestamp": "2026-05-27 17:25:15,740", "level": "INFO", "logger": "flow.validation", "module": "logging_config", "function": "log_gpt_conversation", "line": 403, "message": "{\n  \"event_type\": \"gpt_conversation\",\n  \"task_id\": \"task_Analyze the candidat\",\n  \"conversation_type\": \"task_re_execution\",\n  \"iteration\": 7,\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"system\",\n      \"content\": \"\\n# Role\\nYou are a task re-execution agent. Your role is to generate an improved outcome for the given task by carefully considering the provided context, downstream objectives, previous execution results, and feedback.\\n\\n# Objective & Steps:\\n\\n1. Apply Corrections and Enhancements:\\n   - Address major problems based on previous execution results, and feedback.\\n\\n2. Ensure Completeness:\\n   - Avoid placeholders or incomplete text.\\n   - Your output must meet all requirements of the task.\\n   - Include all necessary details so that the output is self-contained and can be directly used as input for downstream tasks.\\n\\n3. Avoid Repetition:\\n   - Do not repeat verbatim content from previous executions.\\n\\n4. Maintain Precision and Clarity:\\n   - Your output will be used as input for subsequent tasks; therefore, it must be comprehensive and precise.\\n   - **Output the answer only without any jusifications**\\n\\n\\n# Audience:\\nYour output will serve as an improved solution for the task and will undergo further validation and integration into the larger workflow.\\n\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## VERSION 0\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"resume_analysis_steps\\\": [\\n    \\\"1. Parse the resume text to extract relevant information.\\\",\\n    \\\"2. Identify key skills mentioned in the resume.\\\",\\n    \\\"3. List previous work experiences, including company names, job titles, and employment durations.\\\",\\n    \\\"4. Extract educational background, including degrees, institutions, and graduation years.\\\",\\n    \\\"5. Identify any certifications or specific training mentioned.\\\",\\n    \\\"6. Categorize skills into technical skills, soft skills, and domain-specific knowledge.\\\",\\n    \\\"7. Summarize the candidate's overall experience and qualifications.\\\",\\n    \\\"8. Note any quantifiable achievements or metrics mentioned in the resume.\\\",\\n    \\\"9. Identify any potential gaps in experience or skills based on the job description.\\\",\\n    \\\"10. Assess the overall suitability of the candidate based on the resume content.\\\"\\n  ]\\n}\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## FEEDBACK to VERSION 0\\nhere are some feedbacks:\\n- The output provided is a generic list of steps rather than actual extraction of skills, experience, and qualifications from a specific resume.\\n- The task requires a JSON object with the extracted information, not the process steps.\\n- We need to supply a structured JSON schema populated with the candidate’s actual details (or placeholders if details aren’t available).\\n\\nhere are the changes:\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"candidate_name\\\": \\\"\\\",               // Full name of the candidate\\n  \\\"contact_information\\\": {            \\n    \\\"email\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"phone\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"linkedin\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"skills\\\": {\\n    \\\"technical_skills\\\": [             // e.g., programming languages, tools, frameworks\\n      \\\"\\\"\\n    ],\\n    \\\"soft_skills\\\": [                  // e.g., communication, teamwork\\n      \\\"\\\"\\n    ],\\n    \\\"domain_knowledge\\\": [             // e.g., finance, healthcare\\n      \\\"\\\"\\n    ]\\n  },\\n  \\\"work_experience\\\": [                // list each role\\n    {\\n      \\\"company_name\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"job_title\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"start_date\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"end_date\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"responsibilities\\\": [\\n        \\\"\\\"\\n      ],\\n      \\\"achievements\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n          \\\"metric\\\": \\\"\\\"              // e.g., \\\"Reduced server costs by 20%\\\"\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"education\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"degree\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"institution\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"graduation_year\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"certifications_and_training\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"certification_name\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"issuing_organization\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"date_obtained\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"quantifiable_achievements\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"description\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"metric\\\": \\\"\\\"                  // repeated in experience but can include others\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"potential_skill_gaps\\\": [           // based on the job description\\n    \\\"\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"overall_suitability_assessment\\\": \\\"\\\" // A brief summary statement\\n}\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## VERSION 1\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"candidate_name\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n  \\\"contact_information\\\": {\\n    \\\"email\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"phone\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"linkedin\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"skills\\\": {\\n    \\\"technical_skills\\\": [\\n      \\\"\\\"\\n    ],\\n    \\\"soft_skills\\\": [\\n      \\\"\\\"\\n    ],\\n    \\\"domain_knowledge\\\": [\\n      \\\"\\\"\\n    ]\\n  },\\n  \\\"work_experience\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"company_name\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"job_title\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"start_date\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"end_date\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"responsibilities\\\": [\\n        \\\"\\\"\\n      ],\\n      \\\"achievements\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n          \\\"metric\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"education\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"degree\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"institution\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"graduation_year\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"certifications_and_training\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"certification_name\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"issuing_organization\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"date_obtained\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"quantifiable_achievements\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"description\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"metric\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"potential_skill_gaps\\\": [\\n    \\\"\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"overall_suitability_assessment\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n}\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## FEEDBACK to VERSION 1\\nhere are some feedbacks:\\n- The JSON is just an empty schema; no actual resume data has been provided or extracted.\\n- Without the raw resume text, the extractor cannot populate any of these fields.\\n- We need to include the candidate’s resume content (or receive it) before extraction, and then output the populated JSON.\\n\\nhere are the changes:\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"resume_text\\\": \\\"\\\",                            // Please paste the full resume text here\\n  \\\"candidate_name\\\": \\\"\\\",                         // e.g., \\\"Jane Doe\\\"\\n  \\\"contact_information\\\": {\\n    \\\"email\\\": \\\"\\\",                                // e.g., \\\"jane.doe@example.com\\\"\\n    \\\"phone\\\": \\\"\\\",                                // e.g., \\\"+1-555-123-4567\\\"\\n    \\\"linkedin\\\": \\\"\\\"                              // e.g., \\\"linkedin.com/in/janedoe\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"skills\\\": {\\n    \\\"technical_skills\\\": [                       // e.g., [\\\"Python\\\", \\\"AWS\\\", \\\"Docker\\\"]\\n      \\\"\\\"\\n    ],\\n    \\\"soft_skills\\\": [                            // e.g., [\\\"Communication\\\", \\\"Leadership\\\"]\\n      \\\"\\\"\\n    ],\\n    \\\"domain_knowledge\\\": [                       // e.g., [\\\"FinTech\\\", \\\"Healthcare\\\"]\\n      \\\"\\\"\\n    ]\\n  },\\n  \\\"work_experience\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"company_name\\\": \\\"\\\",                       // e.g., \\\"Acme Corp\\\"\\n      \\\"job_title\\\": \\\"\\\",                          // e.g., \\\"Senior Software Engineer\\\"\\n      \\\"start_date\\\": \\\"\\\",                         // e.g., \\\"2019-06\\\"\\n      \\\"end_date\\\": \\\"\\\",                           // e.g., \\\"2023-08\\\" or \\\"Present\\\"\\n      \\\"responsibilities\\\": [\\n        \\\"\\\"                                      // e.g., \\\"Developed microservices in Python\\\"\\n      ],\\n      \\\"achievements\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"\\\",                    // e.g., \\\"Improved API performance\\\"\\n          \\\"metric\\\": \\\"\\\"                          // e.g., \\\"Reduced latency by 40%\\\"\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"education\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"degree\\\": \\\"\\\",                             // e.g., \\\"B.Sc. Computer Science\\\"\\n      \\\"institution\\\": \\\"\\\",                        // e.g., \\\"State University\\\"\\n      \\\"graduation_year\\\": \\\"\\\"                     // e.g., \\\"2018\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"certifications_and_training\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"certification_name\\\": \\\"\\\",                 // e.g., \\\"AWS Certified Solutions Architect\\\"\\n      \\\"issuing_organization\\\": \\\"\\\",               // e.g., \\\"Amazon\\\"\\n      \\\"date_obtained\\\": \\\"\\\"                       // e.g., \\\"2021-05\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"quantifiable_achievements\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"description\\\": \\\"\\\",                        // e.g., \\\"Led a team to launch new feature\\\"\\n      \\\"metric\\\": \\\"\\\"                              // e.g., \\\"Increased user engagement by 25%\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"potential_skill_gaps\\\": [\\n    \\\"\\\"                                          // Based on the job description vs. resume\\n  ],\\n  \\\"overall_suitability_assessment\\\": \\\"\\\"         // A brief summary (e.g., \\\"Strong match for backend role\\\")\\n}\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## VERSION 2\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"resume_text\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n  \\\"candidate_name\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n  \\\"contact_information\\\": {\\n    \\\"email\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"phone\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"linkedin\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"skills\\\": {\\n    \\\"technical_skills\\\": [\\n      \\\"\\\"\\n    ],\\n    \\\"soft_skills\\\": [\\n      \\\"\\\"\\n    ],\\n    \\\"domain_knowledge\\\": [\\n      \\\"\\\"\\n    ]\\n  },\\n  \\\"work_experience\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"company_name\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"job_title\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"start_date\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"end_date\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"responsibilities\\\": [\\n        \\\"\\\"\\n      ],\\n      \\\"achievements\\\": [\\n        {\\n          \\\"description\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n          \\\"metric\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n        }\\n      ]\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"education\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"degree\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"institution\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"graduation_year\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"certifications_and_training\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"certification_name\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"issuing_organization\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"date_obtained\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"quantifiable_achievements\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"description\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"metric\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n    }\\n  ],\\n  \\\"potential_skill_gaps\\\": [\\n    \\\"\\\"\\n  ],\\n  \\\"overall_suitability_assessment\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n}\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## FEEDBACK to VERSION 2\\nhere are some feedbacks:\\n- The current JSON is purely an empty schema and does not extract any data because the actual resume text is missing.\\n- To perform extraction, we must have the candidate’s resume content.\\n- We should prompt for the resume (or include it) so we can populate the fields.\\n\\nhere are the changes:\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"resume_text\\\": \\\"<<Please paste the full resume text here>>\\\",\\n  \\\"candidate_name\\\": \\\"\\\",                         \\n  \\\"contact_information\\\": {\\n    \\\"email\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"phone\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"linkedin\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"skills\\\": {\\n    \\\"technical_skills\\\": [],\\n    \\\"soft_skills\\\": [],\\n    \\\"domain_knowledge\\\": []\\n  },\\n  \\\"work_experience\\\": [],\\n  \\\"education\\\": [],\\n  \\\"certifications_and_training\\\": [],\\n  \\\"quantifiable_achievements\\\": [],\\n  \\\"potential_skill_gaps\\\": [],\\n  \\\"overall_suitability_assessment\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n}\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## VERSION 3\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"resume_text\\\": \\\"<<Please paste the full resume text here>>\\\",\\n  \\\"candidate_name\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n  \\\"contact_information\\\": {\\n    \\\"email\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"phone\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"linkedin\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"skills\\\": {\\n    \\\"technical_skills\\\": [],\\n    \\\"soft_skills\\\": [],\\n    \\\"domain_knowledge\\\": []\\n  },\\n  \\\"work_experience\\\": [],\\n  \\\"education\\\": [],\\n  \\\"certifications_and_training\\\": [],\\n  \\\"quantifiable_achievements\\\": [],\\n  \\\"potential_skill_gaps\\\": [],\\n  \\\"overall_suitability_assessment\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n}\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## FEEDBACK to VERSION 3\\nhere are some feedbacks:\\n- The JSON output is still an empty schema because the actual resume text was not provided, so no skills, experiences, or qualifications could be extracted.\\n- To perform the extraction, we must have the full resume content in the `resume_text` field.\\n\\nhere are the changes:\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"error\\\": \\\"Missing resume_text\\\",\\n  \\\"message\\\": \\\"Please paste the full resume text into the `resume_text` field so that skills, experience, and qualifications can be extracted.\\\",\\n  \\\"schema\\\": {\\n    \\\"resume_text\\\": \\\"<<Paste full resume text here>>\\\",\\n    \\\"candidate_name\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"contact_information\\\": {\\n      \\\"email\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"phone\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"linkedin\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"skills\\\": {\\n      \\\"technical_skills\\\": [],\\n      \\\"soft_skills\\\": [],\\n      \\\"domain_knowledge\\\": []\\n    },\\n    \\\"work_experience\\\": [],\\n    \\\"education\\\": [],\\n    \\\"certifications_and_training\\\": [],\\n    \\\"quantifiable_achievements\\\": [],\\n    \\\"potential_skill_gaps\\\": [],\\n    \\\"overall_suitability_assessment\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n  }\\n}\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## VERSION 4\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"error\\\": \\\"Missing resume_text\\\",\\n  \\\"message\\\": \\\"Please paste the full resume text into the `resume_text` field so that skills, experience, and qualifications can be extracted.\\\",\\n  \\\"schema\\\": {\\n    \\\"resume_text\\\": \\\"<<Paste full resume text here>>\\\",\\n    \\\"candidate_name\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"contact_information\\\": {\\n      \\\"email\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"phone\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n      \\\"linkedin\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"skills\\\": {\\n      \\\"technical_skills\\\": [],\\n      \\\"soft_skills\\\": [],\\n      \\\"domain_knowledge\\\": []\\n    },\\n    \\\"work_experience\\\": [],\\n    \\\"education\\\": [],\\n    \\\"certifications_and_training\\\": [],\\n    \\\"quantifiable_achievements\\\": [],\\n    \\\"potential_skill_gaps\\\": [],\\n    \\\"overall_suitability_assessment\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n  }\\n}\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## FEEDBACK to VERSION 4\\nhere are some feedbacks:\\n- The current output correctly identifies the missing resume text but does not align with the required output format, which expects a JSON ready for data extraction rather than an error wrapper.\\n- We need to produce a JSON structure with a placeholder for `resume_text` (and the other fields) so that once the text is provided, extraction can proceed directly.\\n\\nhere are the changes:\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"resume_text\\\": \\\"<<Please paste the full resume text here>>\\\",\\n  \\\"candidate_name\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n  \\\"contact_information\\\": {\\n    \\\"email\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"phone\\\": \\\"\\\",\\n    \\\"linkedin\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n  },\\n  \\\"skills\\\": {\\n    \\\"technical_skills\\\": [],\\n    \\\"soft_skills\\\": [],\\n    \\\"domain_knowledge\\\": []\\n  },\\n  \\\"work_experience\\\": [],\\n  \\\"education\\\": [],\\n  \\\"certifications_and_training\\\": [],\\n  \\\"quantifiable_achievements\\\": [],\\n  \\\"potential_skill_gaps\\\": [],\\n  \\\"overall_suitability_assessment\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n}\\n```\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": \"---\\n## VERSION 5\\n```json\\n{\\n  \\\"steps\\\": [\\n    {\\n      \\\"step\\\": 1,\\n      \\\"action\\\": \\\"Extract candidate's personal information (name, contact details, etc.) from the resume.\\\",\\n      \\\"expected_output\\\": \\\"Candidate's name, phone number, email address, and LinkedIn profile (if available).\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"step\\\": 2,\\n      \\\"action\\\": \\\"Identify and extract all listed skills from the resume.\\\",\\n      \\\"expected_output\\\": \\\"A comprehensive list of technical and soft skills mentioned in the resume, categorized if possible (e.g., programming languages, tools, frameworks, communication skills).\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"step\\\": 3,\\n      \\\"action\\\": \\\"Extract work experience details from the resume.\\\",\\n      \\\"expected_output\\\": \\\"For each job, extract job title, company name, employment dates, and a summary of responsibilities and achievements.\\\"\\n    },\\n    {\\n      \\\"step\\\": 4,\\n      \\\"action\