tion_id\\\": 8,\\n        \\\"category\\\": \\\"Follow-up\\\",\\n        \\\"question\\\": \\\"Walk me through your approach to solving question 7. What is the time complexity?\\\",\\n        \\\"response\\\": \\\"Candidate’s response here.\\\",\\n        \\\"notes\\\": \\\"\\\"\\n      }\\n    ],\\n    \\\"candidate_questions\\\": {\\n      \\\"prompt\\\": \\\"Do you have any questions for us about the role or company?\\\",\\n      \\\"response\\\": \\\"Candidate’s questions here.\\\"\\n    },\\n    \\\"closing\\\": \\\"Thank you for your time. We will review your responses and get back to you with the next steps.\\\"\\n  }\\n}\\n```\"}"}
