ery using JOINs.\\n      - Score Awarded: 5/5\\n      - Category: SQL\\n   F. Question 6: \\\"Which chart types are suitable for comparing distributions and showing frequency?\\\"\\n      - Candidate Answer: (Based on scoring comments) Correctly identified box plots and histograms.\\n      - Score Awarded: 4/5\\n      - Category: Data Visualization\\n   G. Question 7: \\\"Implement the Fibonacci sequence function.\\\"\\n      - Candidate Answer: (Based on scoring comments) Implemented using dynamic programming (memoization).\\n      - Score Awarded: 5/5\\n      - Category: Coding Exercise\\n   H. Question 8: \\\"Explain why memoization improves the performance of the Fibonacci function.\\\"\\n      - Candidate Answer: (Based on scoring comments) Clearly articulated that memoization improves performance by storing and reusing previously computed results.\\n      - Score Awarded: 5/5\\n      - Category: Follow-up\\n\\n4. Send Initial Interview Email\\n   - (Example)\\n   To: candidate@example.com\\n   Subject: Interview for Data Scientist Position\\n   Body:\\n   \\\"Dear Candidate,\\n\\n   Thank you for your interest in the Data Scientist position at our company. We would like to invite you to a technical interview to assess your skills and experience.\\n\\n   Please find the details of the interview below:\\n\\n   Date: [Date]\\n   Time: [Time]\\n   Platform: [Platform]\\n\\n   We look forward to meeting you.\\n\\n   Sincerely,\\n   [Your Name]\\\"\\n\\n5. Send Follow-up Email (if needed)\\n   - (Example)\\n   To: candidate@example.com\\n   Subject: Reminder: Interview for Data Scientist Position\\n   Body:\\n   \\\"Dear Candidate,\\n\\n   This is a friendly reminder regarding your interview for the Data Scientist position scheduled for [Date] at [Time].\\n\\n   If you have any questions or need to reschedule, please let us know as soon as possible.\\n\\n   We look forward to speaking with you.\\n\\n   Sincerely,\\n   [Your Name]\\\"\\n\\n6. Score Candidate Response